Partner Collaboration

SOTA – OMM Concerto Concert

Published on Jan 25, 2016

SOTA – OMM Concerto Concert


As part of SOTA’s ongoing partnership with the Orchestra of Music Makers (OMM), four SOTA Music students (Kwon Soo Yeon, Joey Lau, Ng Jia Ning and Ronan Lim) performed as soloists at the SOTA – OMM Concerto Concert, Concerti i Solisti IV, on 14 August at SOTA Concert Hall.
